{"tid":638570,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拿玻里絕殺祖記 有機會後上奪冠","createTime":"2018-04-22T23:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T07:25:59.000Z","uid":88110,"like":172,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"5758110729d164bd87f6ff83d12025a2ce275f0b","tid":638570,"uid":88110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T23:21:04.000Z","msg":"傳聞上季完結後，拿玻里一眾主力君子協定留隊，要為球隊奮鬥多一季，結果上半季打出超強戰績，可怕拋唔開祖記<br />\n<br />\n但當中幾位主力其實已接近30歲，包括咸錫，梅頓斯同卡里祖，所以就算無左歐聯後顧，球隊下半季都出現某程度上既崩盤，結果被祖記反壓<br />\n<br />\n不過，憑住尋晚拿玻里作客都靈絕殺對手，令到冠軍出現變數，仲有4場既賽事，祖記只係領先對手1分，但祖記仍要作客苦爭歐聯資格既國米同羅馬，而且對方都係1分不能讓，相反，拿坡里餘下對手最強就是費倫天拿，所以未到最後都唔知鹿死誰手<br />\n<br />\n今年可能係意甲其他球隊最有機會打破壟斷既一年，係各大聯賽冠軍早已定既局面下，意甲既拿玻里將會得到各界的支持，全力向冠軍衝擊，就睇下奇蹟會唔會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb9a05b5f59d7b7f6d7fa6475c6f3b2e4466c5c","tid":638570,"uid":30040,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T23:24:21.000Z","msg":"睇黎要靠希古恩做嘢了"},{"pid":"9db2bb151551fc5bd5bef4bfe16a56341dd50a7f","tid":638570,"uid":14423,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T23:25:28.000Z","msg":"希望國米同羅馬爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22035a7c09f0c474513bab6a82cd7cb9bcc0a9a","tid":638570,"uid":13395,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T23:26:04.000Z","msg":"咸錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望拎番次意甲啦"},{"pid":"76738a072d64b46a26c7fa02493a557f0b45e5c4","tid":638570,"uid":17853,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T23:27:33.000Z","msg":"加油啊拿玻利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ca895febdc1fd0ed39f968790d202c5d9a8feb","tid":638570,"uid":73241,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"rep